title: Mountains
text:
Only registered TrekEarth members may write critiques. Photographer's Note 
Ibiapaba mountain range is near the border of Piaui state. It is in Ceara state and really is a very beautiful mountain range. 
Nobody has marked this note useful daddo (26156) 2015-10-13 4:27 
Hi Maria. A lovely panorama of rolling hills and productive valleys. The light breaking amongst the clouds adds a lot of charm to the scene. Regards. Klaudio. (68856) 2015-10-13 5:47 
Bonjour Maria, J'aime beaucoup l'effet des nuages de pluie au sol. Un très beau point de vue pour nous montrer le phénomène. Un très beau jeu d'ombre et de lumière au sol. Amicalement
